DISCLAIMER:

MindMate Harmony Space is an AI-powered wellness companion designed to provide
emotional support and wellness insights. It is NOT a substitute for professional
mental health treatment.

If you are experiencing a mental health crisis, please:
- Call the National Suicide Prevention Lifeline: 988 (US)
- Text "HELLO" to 741741 (Crisis Text Line)
- Go to your nearest emergency room
- Call emergency services (911 in US)

This application uses AI models to generate recommendations. While efforts have
been made to ensure accuracy and appropriateness, AI-generated responses may not
always be perfect. Use this tool as a complement to, not a replacement for,
professional mental health care.

